## Output Schema

| Column | DuckDB Type | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
| CHROM | VARCHAR | Chromosome of index variant |
| POS | INTEGER | Position of index variant |
| ID | VARCHAR | ID of index variant |
| REF | VARCHAR | Reference allele |
| ALT | VARCHAR | Alternate allele |
| P | DOUBLE | P-value of index variant |
| SP2 | VARCHAR | Clumped variant IDs (comma-separated) |
| NSIG | INTEGER | Number of significant clumped variants (p < p2) |
| TOTAL | INTEGER | Total variants in clump |

One row per clump (index variant).

