## Named Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Default | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|---------|
| `pvalues` | LIST(STRUCT(id VARCHAR, p DOUBLE)) | *(required)* | Variant IDs and p-values |
| `p1` | DOUBLE | 5e-8 | Index variant significance threshold |
| `p2` | DOUBLE | 1e-4 | Clump member significance threshold |
| `r2_threshold` | DOUBLE | 0.1 | Minimum r² to clump with index |
| `window_kb` | INTEGER | 250 | Clumping window in kilobases |
| `pvar` | VARCHAR | auto-discovered | Explicit .pvar/.bim path |
| `psam` | VARCHAR | auto-discovered | Explicit .psam/.fam path |
| `samples` | LIST(VARCHAR) or LIST(INTEGER) | all | Samples for LD computation |
| `region` | VARCHAR | all | Filter to genomic region |

